musalmaan apana dharm to jaanate nahi lekin kaanpi kar hindu se sawaal puchhate rahete he jaraa hamaare bhi sawaalo ke jawaab de do himmat he to . 1) islam banane vaale mohammad ne boodhaape me apane saathi abu-bakar kii 9 saal kii bacchee aaysha se balaatkaar kiya, wo bhi 9 saal kii bacchee se. kya ese balaatkaari kii banaai batoo pe imaan laana sahi he ? 2) mohammad ne apane bete jaid kii bibi jainab se balaatkaar kar shaadi cu kii jaid hijda tha ? yaa mohammad aadat se majaboor tha ? 3) aap bakra id kyon manaate ho ? kyonki aapke kinhi sahab ne allaah ke aadesh pe apane bachche kii qurabaani deni chaahi tab waha bachche kii jagah jaanavar pragat ho gaya , to aap apane bacchon kii qurabaani do naa, jaanavar kii kyon dete ho allaah sachcha hoga to bachche kii jagah jaanavar pragat kar degaa or ye allaah he yaa rakshas jo kun kharabe se prasannn hota he ? 4) ek taraf to murti pujas kii virodh karte ho dusri taraf makka me hajre aswad fattar ko chumne jate ho fattar me vishwaas nahi bolte phir minaa kii jagah fattar ko shaitan samaj fattar cu maarthe ? 5) kyon jab musalmaan makka jate ho to sab mundan kar hindu jaise safed vastra pahante ho ? tawaaf kii puri prakriya hindu kii nakal karte ho phir murti pujas kaa cu virodh karte ho ?? majaar dargaho pe kya hota he ? 6) kyon hinduon kii tarah us jagah kii parikrama karte ho ? jab allaah saatve aasmaan pe baitha he to kaaba ko cu sajadaa, namaskara karte ho ? 7) islam to bahut shanti kaa dharman he (aapke anusaar), to aisa kyon islam main likhaa he ki jo kaphir (gaiyr musalmaan) he unako maar do, aapako 72 huuren milegi ? bhai apni huuron ke chakkar main hamaari jaan kyon lenaa chaahate ho, thodi to insaniyat rakho yaar! 8) quran 2:223 me likhaa he auraton ko kheti kii tarah jaise chaahe istemaal karo quran 33:33 kahati he auraten ghar me bachche paidaa karti rahe or din me 5 baar namaaj phukati rahe kya yahi izzat he aurat kii islam me ? auraton ko burke me ese kaid kar ke rakhte ho aurat na ho koi aate kii bori ho . 9) kyon islam main kaha gaya ki prithvi chokor he, jabaki hindu dharman main prithvi ko gol kaha gaya he, tathaa science pruf kar chukaa he . 10) kyon islam main kaha gaya ki suraj daldal main dub jaataa he, jabaki hindu dharman main likhaa he ki prithvi surya ke chakkar lagaati he ? science bhi pruf kar chukaa he hindu dharman ne duniya ko vimaan shaastra, ayurveda, yoga or hajaaron chize di hai, islam ne duniya ko kya diya, tabaahi or marakaat ke alaava ? 11) 1400 saal pehle aapkaa dharm sthapit hua tha, usase pehle aap kya the ? aapaki ibaadat kaa tarika kya tha ? 12) hamaara hindu dharman hajaaro saal purana he hamaara ram sethu aapane bhi dekha hoga, pani main dubi shri krishna kii nagari bhi dekh lee he, aapke paas kya saboot he ki allaah ne mohammad ko hi bheja tha ? 13) musalmaan jis bhi kshetra men jate he yaa duusare ke yaa khud ke dharm vaale ke saath rahete he vahaan itani ashaanti kyo ho jaati he ? 14) quran 2:260 me allaah ibrahim ko yakeen dilaane ke liye kahata he chaar jaanavar lo phir unki mundia katkar ek-ek kar pahad par rakho phir unhe aawaaj lagaao dekho mundia kaise daudti hui aayegi . sawaal uthta he kya allaah khud ko siddh karne ese phijul ke karname karata rahata he ? kya esa hona sambhav he ? isse kya allaah siddh ho jaayegaa ? 15) agar islam sachcha dharm he to allaah musalamaano ko khatna karke cu nahi bhejtaa ? cu maasoom bachche kaa khatna kar use hindu se musalmaan banaate ho ? 16) kaalpanik qayaamat ke din kabr se kise jinda kiya jaayegaa haddio ko ? cu kii kabr me haddiyaan hi bachati he haddiyaan jananath jaakar kya hurro ke saath disco karegi ?

semifinal kaa samaapan hua - jugal kishor somani     " beeti taahe bisar de , aage kii sud le "  ab samay he rajnatik dalon ko aatanrik samiksha karne kaa - ek duusare par thikra phodne kii vajaay 'aatm chintan' karne kii aavashyaktaa he maaloom padega ki "jo dil khoja aapnaa - mujhase bura na koy" dhyaan rahe " raaj " ke baad " niti " shabd lagata he tab jaakar raajnneeti shuru hoti he . takalif kii baat to yah he ki aaj adhikansh rajaneta ' raajnneeti ' karte hai - raaj'niti' maanate nahin he .       bhartiya rajnatik patal se yah " niti " digbhramit hokar durlabh hoti ja rahi he jaise anek prajatiyon kaa keval vyora maatr hi pustakon main rah gaya he . haan , niti kii tasviir abhi bhi uplabdh he - vaapis is tasviir ko punerjeevit kiya ja saktaa he . nahin to ham bhi ravan - kansa kii shrenee main anke jaayenge . hamen yah nahin bhoolanaa chahie ki aaj ke lagaae paudhe kaa fal hamaari aane vaali peedi khaayegi - spasht he ki fal ke swaadanusaar hi hamaara akalan kiya jayega !!    hamen sudharna hoga , sudhaar karnaa hoga hamaari prayek " niti " kaa . dharm ho yaa karm , vyapaar ho yaa naukari , samaaj ho yaa raaj - sabhi suyogy nitiyon se hi sanchalit hone se hi vikaas kaa maarg khulata he . haan , kisi bhi kaary ke nishpaadan se maarg to koi na koi khulegaa hi lekin vikaas yaa vinaash kaa nirnay to ham swayan hi shuruyaat main hi kar sakate hai yadi ham subuddhi / kubuddhi se soch kar shuruyaat karte hai - kaary kii .    aaj desh " niti " ko taras rahaa he , or yah kaary bhi is desh ke vaasi hi karenge , aisi chizon kaa aayaat nahin hota he , sthai or paripakv samaadhaan hamaari hi mutthi main band he , bas mutthi ko kholane kii kala ke vikaas kii raah dikhaane vaale yug purush kaa sanidhya chahie ....... is mahaan desh main yug purushon kii koi kami nahin he - keval maatr " hanuman shakti " kii tarah jaagrit karnaa he .    " nitivaan " banane ke liye hamen punah ' bhartiya ' bananaa padegaa , hamen hamaare granth khangaalane padenge , guruon kaa aadar karnaa hoga , subah ko subah samajhnaa hoga , dil main suvicharon ko penpaana hoga ...... ham bhul gaye sab kuch - ban baithe madari ke bandar ..... hamen hamaari aatma ko jagaanaa hoga .    haan , yah agrasar hone kaa sahi samay he - shuruyaat to ho chuki - semifinal to ho chukaa . aaj desh ke anek rajya andhere se nikal kar ujaale main saans le rahe hai - fal phool rahe hai - kilkaariyaan maar rahe hai - maan - bahane mangal geet ga rahi hai - pakshi tak chahchaha rahe hai ..... in rajyon ne kisi ko aayaat nahin kiya tha - apni hi mitti kii upaj se nikle bhunre gunaguna rahe hai - in gunagunaate bhunron se hi ye rajya paushit ho rahe hai , garvit ho rahe hai ..... ek ek rajya garvit hoga to kyon nahin puraa desh khushhaal  hoga ? hoga , avashya hoga .....    bas aapako bhartiya hone kaa kartavya nibhaana hoga - maan kii kokh kii laaj rakhni hogi - is dharaa se hue viksit hue apane tan kaa qarz chukaana hoga ....    to , ho jaao taiyaar ...... yahi samay kii pukaar he ...... semifinal ke baad final kii eemaandaaree se taiyaari kerani he .  : jaipur - 7 march 2012

#darbar_kii_kahani  #signora_or_agasta_helicopter  (Part-1) _______________________ maharani signora apane haath peeche baandhe... or pair ko lagbhag patakate hue.... bhare darbar main.... kisi baari bharkam mahishi kii tarah phunfakaarti huyi.... idhar se udhar bechaini se tahal rahi thim. achaanak sabha main maujuud har sabhasad ko aagney netron se ghoorte hue unche asana pe baithe.... oul ke kaan main poochi,... "saare khutte aa gaye?"    oul apni donon bahen chadhaate hue kuch kanphujiyate hue, bolaa,"I think so....!".   signora apane asana pe baith gai. uske baithte hi sabha main itnaa sannata ho gaya ki cheentee bhi khaanse,.. to uski aawaaj nagaade kii tarah lage.   ".......tum sabakaa may itnaa khyaal rakhi, or aaj jab i modi,......shah or swami ke saath mil ke.... hamaare saath ...."tharus" khel rahe hai, to saare ke saare apni punch nichi kar liye ho?   ......... bagal main baithe 'tahamad latel ji' bade pyaar se bole,....  "u '#taharrus' hota he pagali.......  idhar tahamad kaa munh khulaa, udhar signora kii sanasanaati laat padi munh pe, tahamad sahib munh ke bal gire sabha ke bich bich.  ...shabdon ko lagbhag chabate hue, cheekh ke boli signora, "ssaale,... yahan "bhabhi ji ghar pe hai" serial chal rahaa he?? tum sab naakaaron ko ek mudda nahin sujh rahaa he ki media ko kaise bhatakaaya jaae??" _______________________  tabhi chanwar dulaate 'bichudambaram' jhuk ke bole," aap kahen to modi ke chehre pe syaahi phinkava den?"  signora boli," is saale lungi chor kii lungi main... wo bada vaala kekada chodo re, jo hamaare maike se mangavaya tha, khaas isi nalayak ke liye."  .......chanwar or jaldi jaldi dulne laga.   achaanak darban 'munis tiwari' kii aawaaj gunji," kripaya sab log apane apane haath, munh naak aankh, har chhed main spray laga len, khujali team darbar main haaziri dene pahunchne hi vaali he..."  sab log satark hoke baith gaye.  ________________________  khujali team kaa sardaar khujaliwal..., is kaan se us kaan tak khinse niporate hue,.... lagbhag jameen pe lotate hue bolaa,...".....malikaa-e-hindosta signora kii jai ho, tofa kabool karen....."  signora apane nae or kaabil gulam ko tanik ashapurna najaron se dekhte hue boli,"kuch karo, #agasta_mudde se bhatkaao janata ko."  achaanak 'mukesh chhichhoria' bolaa, 'yaar bina mudde ke ab,.. nayaa mudda kaise gadhen'?  tabhi usko pichhawaade se chutki katati huyi khujali team kii rajnartiki.... 'kumari vishwa' ne, aankh maarthe hue adaa se kaha,......"mere jahe-naseeb sardaar kii IIT kii degree isi main he dalle saale, ki bina mudde kaa mudda kaise banaaya jaae..." _____________________  achaanak "sardaar" ne apana suja hua munh uthaa ke kaha,...  "degree se yaad aayaa...., ham log modi kii degree kaa mudda phir se uthaaenge"...."  isi baat pe ghanghor "kaale kute" ne thoothni upar uthaa ke 3 baar bhunk ke is prastaav ke paarit ho jane kii ghoshda kii.   tabhi signora thodaa sanshay main boli ki,.. "agasta' kaa mudda bhul ke modi kii degree pe pil paden, kya itane tuchiye hai "jhakat" log ..?  tabhi haal main.. chirparichit aawaaj gunji,"........ wo "bhakt" hota he pagali."  automatic rispance kii tarah.. matak ke boli signora,"... sahi pakde hai..!"   lekin tabhi histyrian aakhaaj main chikhi,"......pakado saale ko, i shuklava he, ye kahan chupa he hamaari meeting main,,?"  or udhar #shukla_ji roshanadaan se koode, or secondon main chhomantar,.....naarad muni kii tarah ud liye ....... lekin udate udate dimag main yahi chal rahaa tha ki ek bematlab ke mudde se, 'itani badi baat' kaise 'log' bhul jate hai???"
